            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "`'winborder'` has no effect on the completion popup. Not sure if that's intentional.\nI think in Vim this is usually controlled by `'completepopup'`, but that's not ported.\n\n```vim\nvim.fn.complete_info({ \"selected\" })\n```\n\n`preview_*` shouldn't be returned via `selected`; looks like #31180 was meant to fix this.\n\n",
